channel.title: Does High Detail Work on the Client ( 3.2 with Aryan )?
channel.description: I really need to know I wanna play my favorite server in HD but how ?, Idk if that server can be played in HD....

item.title: Does High Detail Work on the Client ( 3.2 with Aryan )?
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

Do you mean HD as in the current RS graphic detail, or just a more detailed environment? If you mean the former, the MoparScape client will not work. If you meant the latter, you simply have to change the code to run the client from “lowmem” to “highmem”.
